      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable ride! While it shows some honest character from its years of service, it remains a solid and functional vehicle. It\u2019s the perfect choice for someone looking for a reliable driver at a great value who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic wear or the occasional minor fix. This car has plenty of life left and is ready for its next chapter with you!",
